title: There's Only One Character On The Creator Says He Wouldn't Kill
text: Part of the fun of a show like The Walking Dead is that you never really feel like any member of the cast is safe. In such a dangerous world, every episode is practically a countdown timer where someone major is going to die eventually, and we just have to wait and find out who's next. Â»
